prompts.text:
The overall style of the artwork is a flat 2D anime style illustration reminiscent of fantasy or supernatural genres.

The background has fantasy architectures and is dominated by deep blues and purples, creating a mysterious and dramatic atmosphere.

A full body image of a female character. The character is standing with her arms spread open.

The character has short silky light purple hair done up in tiny double hair buns, her hair appears ethereal and translucent.

The character's face is serene with a faint smile on her face. She has with light purple eyes, pale skin and striking features.

The character wears a violet military-style coat dress with golden decorum and epaulettes, the coat dress is extremely detailed with intricate patterns and has a side slit. She is also wearing black gloves, thigh boots with reflective purple trims and pantyhose, donning a feather boa draped around her upper arms.
